cosmic-bg: cosmic-bg ( COSMIC session service which applies backgrounds. )
cosmic-bg:
cosmic-bg: * Supports common image formats supported by image-rs
cosmic-bg: * 8 and 10-bit background surface layers
cosmic-bg: * Use of colors and gradients for backgrounds
cosmic-bg: * Per-display background application
cosmic-bg: * Wallpaper slideshows that alternate between backgrounds
cosmic-bg:
cosmic-bg: Homepage: https://github.com/pop-os/cosmic-bg/
